        <a name="HeartDisease"></a> 
        <h3>Heart Disease</h3>
        <p>This section aims to provide a "patient-centred" data and information service to support the drive for improvements in care and services for patients with coronary heart disease. We publish an annual update of statistics each Autumn.</p>
        <p><a href="<%=SubURL%>/Health-Topics/Heart-Disease/">Click here for more Heart Disease information</a></p>                            
